### Front Matter Fields
- `title` (required) - Page title
- `date` (optional) - Publication date (ISO 8601 format)
- `layout` (optional) - Override template selection
- `tags` (optional) - Array of tags
- `toc` (optional) - Generate table of contents
- `draft` (optional) - Skip processing if true
- `pdf` (optional) - Generate PDF version

## Template Selection

Template selection is automatic based on directory:
- `content/posts/` → `post.html` template
- `content/pages/` → `page.html` template
- Root level files → `page.html` template
- Override with `layout` field in front matter

## Site Configuration

[content/site.toml](mdc:content/site.toml) contains site-wide settings:
- Site title
- Base URL (for feeds and absolute links)
- Author information
- Custom metadata
